WARNING
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The user DKM scripts are saved within the iStoaApp folder, upgrading
to a newer version may result in the lost of user files.

Before installing newer iStoaApp version, the user should make a
backup of its script saved in the iStoaApp/ folder.

When installing newer version from the iStoaApp ZIP archive, the user
should request a merging installation, this operation depends on the Archive
software used to install iStoaApp.


HOW TO START
----------------------------------------------------------------------
To start iStoaApp, double click on the file iStoa.app.
